Class: Button

Button

A blank button. Since GUIElement extends Sprite buttons can use a texture that might have text or a symbol. However, clicks are checked against a bounding box and not the texture's pixels. There is also no support for switching textures when the button is moused over or pressed.

new Button(func)

Creates a new Button.
Parameters:
Name Type Description
func function The function to be called when the button is pressed.
Properties:
Name Type Description
func function The function to be called when the button is pressed.
bbox BBox The bounding box used for click/mouseover detection.
drawBG bool Should the background be filled.
color string The background color of the button in its initial state.
upColor string The background color of the button when the mouse is hovering over it.
downColor string The background color of the button when it is pressed.
Source:
  • brine-dev.js, line 2978

Extends

  • GUIElement

                                                        Array

                                                        Button

                                                        A blank button. Since GUIElement extends Sprite buttons can use a texture that might have text or a symbol. However, clicks are checked against a bounding box and not the texture's pixels. There is also no support for switching textures when the button is moused over or pressed.

                                                        new Button(func)

                                                        Creates a new Button.
                                                        Parameters:
                                                        Name Type Description
                                                        func function The function to be called when the button is pressed.
                                                        Properties:
                                                        Name Type Description
                                                        func function The function to be called when the button is pressed.
                                                        bbox BBox The bounding box used for click/mouseover detection.
                                                        drawBG bool Should the background be filled.
                                                        color string The background color of the button in its initial state.
                                                        upColor string The background color of the button when the mouse is hovering over it.
                                                        downColor string The background color of the button when it is pressed.
                                                        Source:
                                                        • brine.js, line 2861

                                                                                                              worldToLocal(x, y) → {Array}

                                                                                                              Returns the given world position as a point within the sprite.
                                                                                                              Parameters:
                                                                                                              Name Type Description
                                                                                                              x number The x coordinate in world space.

                                                                                                              Type
                                                                                                              Array

                                                                                                              Button

                                                                                                              A blank button. Since GUIElement extends Sprite buttons can use a texture that might have text or a symbol. However, clicks are checked against a bounding box and not the texture's pixels. There is also no support for switching textures when the button is moused over or pressed.

                                                                                                              new Button(func)

                                                                                                              Creates a new Button.
                                                                                                              Parameters:
                                                                                                              Name Type Description
                                                                                                              func function The function to be called when the button is pressed.
                                                                                                              Properties:
                                                                                                              Name Type Description
                                                                                                              func function The function to be called when the button is pressed.
                                                                                                              bbox BBox The bounding box used for click/mouseover detection.
                                                                                                              drawBG bool Should the background be filled.
                                                                                                              color string The background color of the button in its initial state.
                                                                                                              upColor string The background color of the button when the mouse is hovering over it.
                                                                                                              downColor string The background color of the button when it is pressed.
                                                                                                              Source:
                                                                                                              • GUI.js, line 515

                                                                                                                                                                    localToWorld(x, y) → {Array}

                                                                                                                                                                    Name Type Description
